  <entry>
    <title>腾讯招聘爬取 - python</title>
    <url>/2019/12/24/%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96-python/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="开搞"><a href="#开搞" class="headerlink" title="开搞"></a>开搞</h3><p>首先分析网页：</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1-1.png" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>乍一看，嗯……，已经分析好了，从列表页用xpath，获取到详情页的id，遍历出来访问就行了。</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.jpg" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>当我把xpath代码写好，取出来正常ID值的时候，我已经以为尘埃落地，直接按照代码运行逻辑走的时候，才发现，我陷入了一个大坑。</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/3.jpg" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>当我正常用get请求url的时候，返回就只有个框架，其余东西啥都没有，我一心想不应该啊，然后看了眼网页源码。</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/5.jpg" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>居然也只是个框架，于是默默的打开了抓包，看看是那个包返回的数据。</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/6.jpg" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>访问了下这条url</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/7.jpg" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>返回了，很经典的json的语法，看来是这条包了，一看链接有个api就应该是请求这条腾讯招聘的接口就能拿到想要的数据。</p>
<p>分析了一下这条url</p>
<p>关键参数就几个，一个毫秒的时间戳13位，一个职务，页数，让接口返回多少条职务信息</p>
<p>就这些参数了，直接请求接口就能返回了。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> json</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> jsonpath</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Date:    2019.12.23</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @QQ_VX:   28441096</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Author:  牛浩东</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Project: 腾讯招聘</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @blog: https://weiyin666.github.io</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">get_time</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    times = time.time()</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> int(round(times * <span class="number">1000</span>))<span class="comment">#定义一个函数get_time</span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>因为需要个时间戳，每次都写太麻烦了，定义了个get_time的函数，用return返回了时间戳，每次用的时候调用这个函数就行。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">get_urls</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url, HEADERS)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text = response.text<span class="comment">#返回为json数据</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text_json = json.loads(text)<span class="comment">#json读取</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    json_lists = jsonpath.jsonpath(text_json,<span class="string">'$..PostId'</span>)<span class="comment">#用jsonpath读取数据</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    json_lists = map(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> url: ul + url + uls, json_lists)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> json_lists</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>因为是json的语法，就用json解析后，使用jsonpath把数据读取出来，然后使用lambda把遍历出来的招聘详情页的id拼接到那个api接口里，获取到正常的api接口后，接下来就是访问解析详情页了。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">details_Page</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url, HEADERS)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text = response.text<span class="comment">#返回为json数据</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text_json = json.loads(text)<span class="comment">#json读取</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    json_title = jsonpath.jsonpath(text_json,<span class="string">'$..RecruitPostName'</span>)<span class="comment">#标题</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    json_Responsibility = jsonpath.jsonpath(text_json,<span class="string">'$..Responsibility'</span>)<span class="comment">#职责</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#只提取俩个数据，其他需要什么数据按照上面提取json的属性值就行了</span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>requests库get请求接口，返回数据json读取，然后jsonpath提取json数据里的属性值，现在该有的都有了，接下来就是保存了。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">save_details</span><span class="params">(title,Responsibility)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    fout.write(<span class="string">'职位名称:'</span> + title + <span class="string">' -- '</span> + <span class="string">'职责:'</span> + Responsibility +<span class="string">'\n'</span>)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>保存一下数据，但是，处理数据的时候发现，json取到的属性值他不规则，但是一个个去处理文本比较麻烦。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">str_rule</span><span class="params">(rule)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    rules = str(rule).replace(<span class="string">"['"</span>,<span class="string">''</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    rules = str(rules).replace(<span class="string">"']"</span>,<span class="string">''</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    rules = str(rules).replace(<span class="string">"\\n"</span>,<span class="string">''</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    rules = str(rules).replace(<span class="string">"\\r"</span>,<span class="string">''</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> rules</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后写了个函数str_rule，直接把替换的规则写好，传入json取出来的属性传入函数里，使用里面的替换规则走一遍，数据就处理好了，正常返回就行了。</p>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>比昨天的电影天堂麻烦，但是数据好处理，json直接读属性，比较规则的平台。</p>
<p> 今天的笔记分享到这里就结束了。</p>
]]></content>
