    <title>电影天堂爬取-python</title>
    <url>/2019/12/22/%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96-python/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="获取单页的电影详情"><a href="#获取单页的电影详情" class="headerlink" title="获取单页的电影详情"></a>获取单页的电影详情</h2><p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1.png" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>很明显看出来list<em>23</em>后面的数字是代表第几页</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> lxml <span class="keyword">import</span> etree</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">遍历出单页所有的电影详情的链接</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Date:    2019.12.22</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @QQ_VX:   28441096</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Author:  牛浩东</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Project: 天堂之家电影爬取</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @blog: https://weiyin666.github.io</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">HEADERS =&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="string">'User-Agent'</span>: <span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/78.0.3904.97 Safari/537.36'</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">get_urls</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url,HEADERS)<span class="comment">#get请求url</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text = response.text<span class="comment">#获取响应的返回</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    html = etree.HTML(text)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    detail_urls = html.xpath(<span class="string">"//table[@class='tbspan']//a/@href"</span>)<span class="comment">#使用xpath定位元素</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> detail_url <span class="keyword">in</span> detail_urls:<span class="comment">#遍历所有的a标签的herf属性</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        print(<span class="string">'https://dytt8.net'</span> + detail_url)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    get_urls(<span class="string">'https://dytt8.net/html/gndy/dyzz/list_23_1.html'</span>)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>首先定义HEADERS，创建函数get_urls传入参数url，get发送请求获取响应，使用Xpath定位元素</p>
<p><img src="https://weiyi5.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/2.png" alt="咸鱼 blog"></p>
<p>因为浏览器点击超链接跳转电影详情页的时候会自动添加前缀<a href="https://dytt8.net，所以我们打印使用xpath获取到的值给他拼接一个前缀" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://dytt8.net，所以我们打印使用xpath获取到的值给他拼接一个前缀</a></p>
<h2 id="获取多个页面所有电影详情"><a href="#获取多个页面所有电影详情" class="headerlink" title="获取多个页面所有电影详情"></a>获取多个页面所有电影详情</h2><p>写爬虫不可能每次爬一个列表页，那么接下来就遍历多个列表页的所有电影详情的链接</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> lxml <span class="keyword">import</span> etree</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">获取多个列表页的所有电影详情的链接</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Date:    2019.12.22</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @QQ_VX:   28441096</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Author:  牛浩东</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @Project: 天堂之家电影爬取</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">     @blog: https://weiyin666.github.io</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">HEADERS =&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="string">'User-Agent'</span>: <span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/78.0.3904.97 Safari/537.36'</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ul = <span class="string">'https://dytt8.net'</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">get_urls</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url,HEADERS)<span class="comment">#get请求url</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text = response.text<span class="comment">#获取响应的返回</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    html = etree.HTML(text)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    detail_urls = html.xpath(<span class="string">"//table[@class='tbspan']//a/@href"</span>)<span class="comment">#使用xpath定位元素</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    detail_urls = map(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> url:ul+url,detail_urls)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    lambda表达式相当于一个匿名函数</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    等于</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    def abc():#定义一个函数</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">        return ul+url</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    index = 0#定义一个下标</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    for detail_url in detail_urls:#遍历所有详情的url</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">        detail_url = abc(detail_url)#调用abc函数</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">        detail_urls[index] = detail_url</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">        index += 1</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    """</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> detail_urls</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">spider</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    爬虫入口</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    """</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    base_url = <span class="string">'https://dytt8.net/html/gndy/dyzz/list_23_&#123;&#125;.html'</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">3</span>):<span class="comment">#range第二个数字只会指定到-1的位数也就是2</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        url = base_url.format(x)<span class="comment">#构建好了你想获取列表页</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        detail_urls = get_urls(url)<span class="comment">#调用函数get_ulrs把详情页列表url传进去</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> detail_url <span class="keyword">in</span> detail_urls:<span class="comment">#遍历每一个详情页的所有电影链接</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">            print(detail_url)<span class="comment">#打印出所有的url</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    spider()</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="获取每个详情页的信息"><a href="#获取每个详情页的信息" class="headerlink" title="获取每个详情页的信息"></a>获取每个详情页的信息</h3><p>每个列表页和列表页内所有的电影url搞定了接下来就是请求电影详情页获取电影详细信息</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">Details_page</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url,headers=HEADERS)<span class="comment">#访问详情页</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    text = response.content.decode(<span class="string">"gbk"</span>, errors=<span class="string">'ignore'</span>)<span class="comment">#解析返回的详情页，使用gbk解码</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    html = etree.HTML(text)<span class="comment">#创建xpath</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    title = html.xpath(<span class="string">"//div[@class='title_all']//font[@color='#07519a']/text()"</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>]<span class="comment">#使用xpath语法获取详情页需要的内容,如标题，下载链接，演员等...,一个例子其他照葫芦画瓢</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    print(title)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    打印出电影详情页的title</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    """</span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>获取到了电影详情页的内容，那么接下来就是写到本地txt文件了。</p>
<h3 id="保存本地txt文档"><a href="#保存本地txt文档" class="headerlink" title="保存本地txt文档"></a>保存本地txt文档</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fout = open(<span class="string">"电影天堂爬取.txt"</span>, <span class="string">"w"</span>, encoding=<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)<span class="comment">#先创建个txt文本,写入文本切记设置一个编码格式，utf-8的编码</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">save_movie</span><span class="params">(title,img)</span>:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    <span class="string">"""</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    save_movie爬取到详情信息调用这个函数传入参数，需要那些详情信息自行传入参数，这里做了个例子之传入了标题和海报</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    fout.write中\n是换行符的意思,没有的话就会全部连在一块，看不了</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">    """</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    fout.write(<span class="string">'电影名称：'</span>+title+<span class="string">'----'</span>+<span class="string">'电影海报:'</span>+img+<span class="string">'\n'</span>)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>到这里就彻底结束了，码了好几个小时的代码，写个笔记，在熟悉一下。</p>
]]></content>
